reviewText: As advertised, fast delivery, very pleased!

Westinghouse Studio One productions originally shown on Monday 10:00 - 11:00 CBS 1948-1958. The Willow Cabin with Charlton Heston and Priscilla Gillette is a tragic romance between an American surgeon and a wild young British actress. Only his wife and WW II can keep them apart. You just can't beat these classic television shows.
